commit.message:
Fix layout

Fixes #227
Update pot file and German translation
Fixed a few error message formattings.
fixed I18N_ARGUMENT_MISSING string showing up in the error dialog;
Apply i18n to percent values

Improve string formatting

- Adopt strings to follow KDE HIG
- Improve accessibility via using dedicated ellipsis character
- Fix typos
- Improve grammar
finish Py2 to 3 transition

t_defaultprovider: properly delete created file

rmdir() only deletes an empty directory. As files were created within
this directory the test would always fail.
This wasn't showing as it would nearly always be skipped as the
directory is still left over from the first failed run.
Remove extra header, recreated html pages

Add mask argument to drawImage call in reportlab converter.

Now it renders pngs with transparent background. Fixes #218
Bump the copyright year of the manual
Add a valid page size to the default gtmpl template.
Add information about logo with weasyprint, part 1
Update the generation timestamp of the html manual
Added template for XRechnung version 3.0.1

Remove existing XRechnung file before copy to overwrite.

QFile::copy does not overwrite existing files

Add little script to check if all images in manual are present

It greps all images from the adoc source and checks if in the images
dir are screenshot files for all languages
Update of screenshots - kudos to Ronald Stroethoff

Omit BUILD_HOST_NAME for reproducible builds

Distributions that want reproducible builds, set the SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH
environment variable. In this case, we should not record the build
host name to allow for bit-identical rebuilds elsewhere.

This patch was done while working on reproducible builds for openSUSE.
Update manual from Ronald
Remove logs that are commented out

Remove/comment out some unused QStrings

Those are non-trivial values which cause runtime overhead

Use QString() constructor for constructing empty string

The only difference is that this string would be null, but AFAICS that isn't a problem here
Port away from deprecated QFlags constructor
Port away from deprecated QLatin1Literal
Fix CMake warning about specifiying minimum version after project call

Be more robust if neither .git nor .tag file can not be found.

Before, cmake was bailing out. Fixes #211
Updated dutch UI translations
Manual: Fixed a asciidoc error
Manual: Update the translation files
